---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TryOnStudio from '../components/TryOnStudio.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Try On | AI Beauty Stylist"
  description="上传自拍、获取 AI 面部与色彩诊断、查看 3 套更适合你的妆容方案。"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container section-copy narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Try On</span>
      <h1>从“上传照片”到“选方案”，先把 MVP 核心闭环打通。</h1>
      <p>
        这个页面承接 PRD 里的核心价值：不是给你滤镜，而是先判断、再推荐、再引导进入教程与工具购买决策。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <TryOnStudio />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
